**NOTE:** `settings_raw` and `data_stream_name` are write-only and are not returned by the CCR info API. After import they are empty in Terraform state. Add them to your configuration manually if you use them, matching the values already applied in Elasticsearch.

**NOTE:** `data_stream_name` is ForceNew. When importing a data stream follower, set `data_stream_name` in configuration **before** import if possible. If you add a non-null `data_stream_name` after import (when state is null), Terraform plans a replacement even though the follower already tracks the correct data stream.
